Welcome to the redesigned Watch TCM app! We ve made some major updates to our app in design stability and features. Some of the new and improved features include: New and improved design: Now find movies live broadcasts and movie information faster and easier Picture in picture Users on supported iPads can continue watching Watch TCM films while browsing the web or using other apps. Apple Single Sign on integration with supported providers Added support for AirPlay and Mirroring Improved Search Improved Watchlist Users can play or add a movie to a Watchlist on one device and resume watching from a different device. Expiring soon labeling for titles leaving the service. Browse by TCM Collections Quickly access On Demand films by popular themes such as Star of the Month Noir Alley 31 Days of Oscar and more. Thank you for your continued support and patience for Watch TCM.

Thank you all for your continued support of Watch TCM. Here are some exciting new features in this major Fall 2015 release: Improved clips quality. We worked hard to upgrade some of the video of our short form clips. You ll see noticeable improvements immediately especially in clips related to the current day s programming. Improved Archive Image thumbnails and aspect ratios now see our stunning Archives with better detail Pinch and zoom now enabled on all Image Archives! Video Playback: Now you get volume control and 30 second rewind capabilities. New: Clip Promo and Trailer information for iPad: Select a clip and get information on all of our free short form material in Watch TCM. Improved Watchlist and Search Views for iPad. Improved fluidity in the main On Demand carousel. New beautiful load animation Many design tweaks and bug fixes. Please share the fun and tell your friends about WATCH TCM and thanks for all your support.

Thank you for the great feedback and comments for Watch TCM we really appreciate the great suggestions and ratings as we continue to improve. Here s what s in this update: Schedule Themes: Get a quick view of TCM nightly themes by tapping the info button in our Schedule Page. Now you can learn every prime time theme at a glance. Clips and Trailers: We ve changed some headers to more accurately describe clips playing on TCM Today and new ones just added Sign in design and stability improvements Design Improvements Thanks again for all your support of Watch TCM.
